---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="🤝 Why Sponsor? - Manuel Gil - Software Developer & Open Source Advocate">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-20">
    <section class="flex items-center justify-center py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-6xl font-bold text-transparent"
        >
          Why Sponsor?
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-zinc-400">
          Sponsoring my work means directly supporting <strong class="text-zinc-200"
            >open-source innovation</strong
          > and <strong class="text-zinc-200">developer empowerment</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">🎯 Sponsors Get</h2>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🎖 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Recognition</strong> – Your name/company featured in my
            projects and social media.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🚀 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Priority Feature Requests</strong> – Influence the roadmap
            of my tools.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🤝 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Exclusive Access</strong> – Early access to new features
            and project updates.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🎤 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Private Sessions</strong> – 1:1 discussions about tools,
            best practices, and development strategies.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-bold mb-6 text-zinc-200">
          🔥 Let's build the future of development together.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/ManuelGil"
          class="inline-block text-primary transition-colors hover:text-primary-dark"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Become a Sponsor →
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
